* FILENAME:         NE68130.CIR
* NEC PART NUMBER:  NE68130
* LAST MODIFIED:    10/96
* BIAS CONDITIONS:  Vce=2.5V to 8V, Ic=0.3mA to 10mA
* FREQ RANGE:       0.05GHz to 3GHz
*
*                            CCBpkg
*                    .-------||--------.  
*                    |          CCB    |   
*                    |      .--||---.  |       COLLECTOR
* BASE               |      |        | |             
*                    |      |   /----o-o-----o--Lcx--o  
*            o--Lbx--o-LB---o--|Q1   |       |       
*                    |      B   \   --       --      
*                    |          |   -- CCE   -- CCEpkg
*                    --CBEpkg E o----'       |           
*                    --         |            |      
*                    |         LE            |       
*                    `----------o------------'       
*                               |                   
*                               Lex            
*                               |  
*                               o EMITTER
*                                
*       CCB    = 0.07pF          LB  = 0.52nH             
*       CCE    = 0.01pF          LE  = 1.18nH           
*       CCBpkg = 0.12pF          Lbx = 0.2nH          
*       CCEpkg = 0.16pF          Lcx = 0.8nH             
*       CBEpkg = 0.04pF          Lex = 0.2nH          
*
*                   c b e
.SUBCKT NE68130/CEL 2 1 3
Q1  5 7 8 NE68100
CCB 7 5 0.07E-12
CCE 5 8 0.01E-12
LE  8 6 1.18E-9
LB  4 7 0.52E-9
CCBPKG 4 5 0.12E-12
CCEPKG 5 6 0.16E-12
