LCX 5 2 0.8E-9
LEX 6 3 0.2E-9
.MODEL NE68100 NPN 
+( IS=2.70e-16   BF=185.0         NF=1.02        VAF=15.0         IKF=0.055
+ ISE=1.77e-11   NE=2.10          BR=1.0         NR=1.0           VAR=0.0
+ IKR=0.0        ISC=0.0          NC=2.0         RE=0.6           RB=12.0
+ RBM=3.70       IRB=1.20e-5      RC=8.0         CJE=1.20e-12     VJE=0.770
+ MJE=0.50       CJC=0.80e-12     VJC=0.270      MJC=0.560        XCJC=0.0
+ CJS=0.0        VJS=0.750        MJS=0.0        FC=0.50          TF=14.0e-12
+ XTF=3.0        VTF=25.0         ITF=0.10       PTF=0.0          TR=0.30e-9
+ EG=1.11        XTB=0.0          XTI=3.0        KF=0.0           AF=1.0 )
